description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '15 Minute Guided Breathing For Calm and Restful Sleep' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
